sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant F as Founder
    participant CC as Claude Code
    participant M as kipi-mcp server.py
    participant H as Harness module<br/>(linter, scorer, etc)
    participant FS as Filesystem<br/>(canonical, bus, db)

    F->>CC: "lint this draft for voice"
    CC->>M: kipi_voice_lint(text)
    M->>H: linter.voice_lint(text)
    H->>H: regex match banned phrases
    H->>H: check sentence length variance
    H->>H: detect emdashes
    H->>FS: read voice-dna reference
    H-->>M: VoiceLintResult(passed=False, violations=[...])
    M-->>CC: JSON result with pass/fail + violations
    CC->>F: shows specific violations + line numbers

    Note over H: Pure Python.<br/>No LLM in the loop<br/>for the validation step.

    F->>CC: "score this lead"
    CC->>M: kipi_score_lead(attrs, signals)
    M->>H: scorer.score_lead(...)
    H->>FS: read scoring weights from registry
    H->>H: deterministic math
    H-->>M: {score: 78, tier: "hot", reasons: [...]}
    M-->>CC: JSON result
    CC->>F: "Score: 78 (hot). Top reasons: ..."
